{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setAdvertisingId:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"advertisingId","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"advertisingId","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The advertising identifier string, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" to clear it."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK does not collect IDFA automatically. The integrator is responsible for"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"requesting user consent via "},{"code":"ATTrackingManager.requestTrackingAuthorization","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"passing the resulting identifier to the SDK."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pass "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", an empty string, or the zero UUID"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"\"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\""},{"type":"text","text":") to clear the identifier on the backend."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The zero UUID is what "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ASIdentifierManager.advertisingIdentifier"},{"type":"text","text":" returns when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tracking is denied or restricted — the SDK normalizes it to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" automatically.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Behavior:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Fire-and-forget: no completion handler. The SDK retries on transient failures.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Deduplicated: repeated calls with the same value do not produce additional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"network requests."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The value is persisted locally only after a successful send and read back on","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"subsequent launches for the dedupe check."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default the IDFA is sent to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"https:\/\/tracking.svc-nue.pushwoosh.com\/api\/v2\/device-api\/setMADID"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"You can override the tracking endpoint via the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Pushwoosh_TRACKING_URL"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Info.plist key (useful for on-premise deployments and integration testing)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"App-Store-submission-requirement","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"App Store submission requirement"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Apple requires that any tracking domain be declared in the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"integrator’s","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"app-level "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PrivacyInfo.xcprivacy"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"syntax":"xml","code":["<key>NSPrivacyTracking<\/key>","<true\/>","<key>NSPrivacyTrackingDomains<\/key>","<array>","    <string>tracking.svc-nue.pushwoosh.com<\/string>","<\/array>"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you override ","type":"text"},{"code":"Pushwoosh_TRACKING_URL","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", list ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"your","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" host instead. Apps that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"ship without this declaration will be blocked by iOS on non-authorized devices"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and may face App Store review issues."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You must also add ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSUserTrackingUsageDescription"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Info.plist"},{"text":" — it is the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"text displayed in the ATT consent prompt.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"code":["import AppTrackingTransparency","import AdSupport","","ATTrackingManager.requestTrackingAuthorization { status in","    if status == .authorized {","        let idfa = ASIdentifierManager.shared().advertisingIdentifier.uuidString","        Pushwoosh.configure.setAdvertisingId(idfa)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To clear:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["Pushwoosh.configure.setAdvertisingId(nil)"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setadvertisingid:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the advertising identifier (IDFA) for the device."}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setAdvertisingId:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setAdvertisingId:","roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setAdvertisingId:"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setAdvertisingId:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor